  Embedded-iot.net/dht11/dataCollector.php)

  Uses POST command to send DHT data to a designated website
  The circuit:
  * DHT
  * Post to Domain

   Computer Engineer: Stephen Borsay
   Embedded-iot.net
   www.udemy.com/all-about-arduino-wireless
   https://www.hackster.io/detox
